		<title>Capchase Raises $200M+ to Expand Financing Platform</title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/capchase-raises-200m-to-expand-financing-platform/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ekemini]]></dc:creator>
